data.hidden_message: There's a painting of me. I don't understand. It's not me but it's labelled with my name.
Day one. People keep behaving strangely and acting like they know me, know my habits. Very suspicious. I haven't drank since highschool. This is how I always dress. I don't understand.
I know something is wrong. My appearance wasn't a mistake. Did seeing me dressed as this scare you captain? What happened to Ulyssa?
Whoever is keeping me here, I will kill you. I can only hope I haven't dropped my facade for you yet.
